data_analysis.dataDescription: This dataset contains 102 metrics. There are 12 time-series metrics that show trends over time. There are 42 grouped metrics that can be broken down by categories. There are 48 summary/total metrics. There are 15 complex metrics with embedded sub-metrics or account-level breakdowns. Currency metrics include: totalGrossSales, totalShippingIncome, sales, totalGrossSalesChangePercentage, totalNetSalesChangePercentage, netSalesByConnector, cashOnHand, cashOnHandChangePercentage, cashOnHandAmounts, creditCardBalance, creditCardBalances, grossProfit, grossProfitMargin, grossProfits, changeInCash, changeInCashChangePercentage, changesInCash, freeCashYield, netSales, totalNetSales, totalNewCustomerTotalNetSales, totalReturningCustomerTotalNetSales, customerAqCost, amazonBalance, dataBySalesConnectors.grossSales, dataBySalesConnectors.grossSalesPeriodAgo, dataBySalesConnectors.grossSalesChangePercentage, dataBySalesConnectors.netSales, dataBySalesConnectors.netSalesPeriodAgo, dataBySalesConnectors.netSalesChangePercentage, customerAqCostPercentageChange, totalSalesGeneralAdministrativeExpenses, totalSalesGeneralAdministrativeExpensesChangePercentage. Percentage metrics include: totalOrdersChangePercentage, contributionMarginPercentage, contributionMarginRatio, netMERGrowthPercentage, burnRates, contributionMarginPercentages, aMerGrowthPercentage, newCustomerAOVPercentageChange, burnRate. Count metrics include: totalRefunds, totalOrders, orders, totalNewCustomerOrders, totalReturningCustomerOrders, totalNewCustomersCount, totalFreight. Data appears to be from 2025. Use 2025 for date ranges unless user specifies otherwise.
